dict.string: Local Pub in the Gamlestan area that's been housing Bellevue Jazz for a couple of years now. You'll find the concerts in the cellar. Upstairs there's a charming bar filled with everything you could A1:D18 for. Ticets are purchased in the door, upon arrival.
A beautiful cultural center in the middle of Gothenburg City. Here you'll be able to experience everything from a smashing vegan brunch to poetry readings and heavy metal. Always free entrance.
Hip venue in the Majorna area that presents a wide array of artists and has an awesome restaurant.
A really cool cutural house in the east parts of the city. It was used as a prison until 1997 but is now a fully equipped and modern concert venue.
A beautiful church located in the Gamlestan area. They have been a part of the festival for the last two years. Free Entrance!
A church in the eastern parts of Gothenburg. They've been a part of the festival for the last two years. Free entrence!
A musicians collective that hangs out in the old brick-houses by Gamlestans Fabriker. It's mostly used for band practice and studio recordings so public concerts here are a rare but beautiful thing.
Restaurant and bar run the the Italian Association in Gothenburg.
A beautiful venue in the center of Gothenburg. Great food and drinks
Really cool theatre by Järntorget in the center of Gothenburg. Have at bite to eat in their great vegetarian restaurant.
One of the studios in the artsy area of Konstepidemin in Gothenburg. Located near Linnégatan wich is a street full of great bars and restaurants.
Here you'll find the best tacos in the city along with great live music in a relaxed setting. Located on the superhip and lively street Andra Långgatan.
Really central and diverse venue on the cool street Andra Långgatan in the center of Gothenburg.
The biggest, oldest and most renown venue for jazz and improvised music in Gothenburg. They been presenting everything from free jazz to blues and dixie since the 70's.
A relatively new venue in Majorna near the beautiful area around Älvsborgsbron. You buy your tickets upon arrival, in the door.
Fantastic restaurant, bar and concert venue in the heart of Gotheburg.
The Gothenburg Rowing Associasions club house. Beautifully located in the archipelago.
